# ==AUTO== Automatically translated
msgid ""
"Field names are case-insensitive. Supported formats: mp3, ogg, flac, "
"opus, aac/m4a and others supported by mutagen. A <b>default</b> is "
"strongly recommended — tags may be absent or the file may not be a "
"supported audio format."
